Sentencas: For the first time, A2BO4 type high-entropy oxide is applied to SOFC cathode.
Titulo: A novel high-entropy cathode with the A2BO4-type structure for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In this paper, a (La0.2Pr0.2Nd0.2Sm0.2Gd0.2)2CuO4 high-entropy oxide (HE-LCO) is synthesized.
Titulo: A novel high-entropy cathode with the A2BO4-type structure for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The phase structure, DC conductivity, high-temperature thermal expansion and electrochemical performance of HE-LCO are studied in detail.
Titulo: A novel high-entropy cathode with the A2BO4-type structure for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: HE-LCO crystallizes in tetragonal symmetry with space group I4/mmm.
Titulo: A novel high-entropy cathode with the A2BO4-type structure for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The thermal expansion coefficient of HE-LCO is 12.19 x 10-6 K-1 in the range of 100-800 degrees C, which is compatible with GDC electrolyte.
Titulo: A novel high-entropy cathode with the A2BO4-type structure for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The area-specific resistance (ASR) of HE-LCO cathode is 0.52 Omega cm2, and the peak power density of the anode support fuel cell attains 528 mW cm-2 at 700 degrees C.
Titulo: A novel high-entropy cathode with the A2BO4-type structure for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In addition, the dissociation of molecular oxygen on HE-LCO cathode is recognized to be the rate-limiting step of the ORR kinetics.
Titulo: A novel high-entropy cathode with the A2BO4-type structure for solid oxide fuel cells
